OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'It's classless' - using   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fice cream to help people   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftalk about grief           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Artist Annie Nicholson believes a good 
OL,6, place to start a conversation about    
OL,7, loss is over a scoop of ice cream. Her 
OL,8, work has centred around grief since    
OL,9, losing members of her family in a      
OL,10, tragic accident 11 years ago.          
OL,12,FMini milks, choc ices, a 99 with a     
OL,13,Fflake - and a chat about loss.         
OL,15,FThe sweet, soft, sugary taste of ice   
OL,16,Fcream does not usually sit alongside   
OL,17,Fthe pain and devastation of grief. Yet 
OL,18,FAnnie Nicholson's ice cream van was    
OL,19,Fdesigned to break a taboo.             
